Package: Scale
Title: Scale x and y coordinates
Version: 0.0.1.0001
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Flippie",
           family = "Coetser",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "Flippie.Coetser@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0549-9245"))
Description: 
    When using R plot function, the X and Y coordinates are not always scaled to the same scale. 
    This package provides a function to scale the X and Y coordinates so that a more realistic output is presented.
